      "message": "[major] Line 746: 🟡 The repeating request is submitted with `null` as the CaptureCallback, but the original session setup uses a `captureCallback` that handles codec start and key frame insertion. Replacing the repeating request with one that has a null callback means codec-start logic (e.g., `startMediaCodecIfNeeded`) won\u0027t fire if a zoom change happens before the codec is started. Consider storing and reusing the original `CaptureCallback`.",
