      "message": "[minor] Line 105: 🟡 `startProgressiveZoom` captures `focusX` and `focusY` at the time of the long press and uses them for the entire animation duration. If the user moves their finger after the long press begins, the zoom focus point remains fixed at the original position, which may feel unnatural. Consider updating the focus coordinates if a move event occurs during the progressive zoom.",
